data.description: 5 Longview is a great place to call home with lakeviews, southern exposure and a location less than 5 minutes to shopping, restaurants, Table Rock Lake and marinas. You'll enjoy the open concept of the great room, dining, kitchen and nook - all with views of Table Rock Lake.  The gourmet Kitchen features a large island, with cabinets galore and an abundance of pantry space with slide out shelving. The Great Room features a vaulted ceiling and a fireplace, with Ozark natural stone. The main-level Master Bedroom is spacious and offers a large U- shaped walk-in closet, and a bathroom that is an oasis featuring twin vanities, a jetted tub and a large walk-in shower.  On the lower level are two guest bedrooms, a family room and another bath with two sinks.
